    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="section-head">
        <div class="eyebrow"><span class="dot"></span>06 &middot; Roadmap</div>
        <div>
          <h2>Three phases. Shipping order is not negotiable.</h2>
          <p class="lede" style="margin-top:16px">
            Phase 1 has to stand on its own before anything else ships. Fast, correct, drop-in. The
            rest is upside.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="roadmap">
        <div class="phase">
          <div class="ph-tag">
            <span class="ph-num">Phase 01</span>
            <span class="tag accent">In flight</span>
          </div>
          <h3>Drop-in replacement</h3>
          <div class="ph-time">~6 weeks &middot; Q2 2026</div>
          <ul>
            <li>inotify + sd_journal log watching</li>
            <li>Top 20 filters &middot; sshd priority 1</li>
            <li>nftables &middot; iptables &middot; ipset backends</li>
            <li><code>--import-config</code> migration tool</li>
            <li>Reproducible musl builds, 4 archs</li>
            <li>Benchmark suite vs fail2ban</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="phase">
          <div class="ph-tag">
            <span class="ph-num">Phase 02</span>
            <span class="tag">Next</span>
          </div>
