          <div class="ph-time">8&ndash;12 weeks after ph. 1</div>
          <ul>
            <li>eBPF/XDP packet drop at NIC driver</li>
            <li>Encrypted gossip ban sharing (SWIM)</li>
            <li>Hot-reload config &middot; zero downtime</li>
            <li>GeoIP / ASN filter conditions</li>
            <li>Built-in Prometheus endpoint</li>
            <li>Adaptive anomaly thresholds</li>
