          <ul>
            <li>Authenticated REST API for SIEM/SOAR</li>
            <li>Optional web dashboard (separate binary)</li>
            <li>deb &middot; rpm &middot; apk &middot; pkg &middot; homebrew</li>
            <li>Cloud backends: AWS SG &middot; GCP &middot; Azure</li>
            <li>Signed audit trail for compliance</li>
            <li>Restricted DSL for user filters</li>
          </ul>
